This article is a Presidential Memorandum from March 18, 2016, in which President Barack Obama delegates authority to the Director of National Intelligence regarding the Hizballah International Financing Prevention Act of 2015. The memorandum states that the President is delegating to the Director of National Intelligence the functions and authorities vested in the President by sections 101, 201, and 202 of the Act. The President also authorizes and directs the Director of National Intelligence to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.